# ToolsHub Worker -- Cloudflare Secrets Reference
# Set each secret with: npx wrangler secret put SECRET_NAME

# GROQ_API_KEY -- Groq API key. Required: YES.
# GITHUB_MODELS_TOKEN -- GitHub PAT (models:read). Required: YES for Layer 2 fallback (models.github.ai/inference/chat/completions) and fan-out.
# TAVILY_API_KEY -- Tavily search. Required: YES for Search tool.
# FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT -- Firebase admin JSON (1 line). Required: YES (enforces usage limits).
# SENTRY_DSN -- Sentry DSN. Required: NO.
# ADMIN_UID -- Admin endpoint guard token. Required: NO.
# RAZORPAY_KEY_ID -- Razorpay Key ID. Required: YES for payments.
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET -- Razorpay Secret. Required: YES for payments.
# RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET -- Webhook signing secret. Required: YES (prevents webhook spoofing).

# Cloudflare Bindings (in wrangler.toml, NOT here): AI, VECTORIZE, RATE_LIMIT_KV
